iates. In addition, it offers drug and cosmetic colours for tablet coatings, compressed tablets, syrups, hard and soft gelatin capsules, toiletries, skin-care products, water-based make-ups, lipsticks, nail polishes, pencils, foundations, and lip glosses; and natural food colours. The company also exports its products. Dynemic Products Limited was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Ahmedabad, India."}}